This FCC applies towards the WLA532-US, WLA532-WW, and the WLA532-IL.
"PCB MADE IN CHINA", "370HR", "P/N: 142000000381A REV: 0B", and :''Juniper Networks'' logo is silkscreened on the main board.
The Flash chip used appears to be a 32MB MX29GL256FHT2I-90Q.
The 5GHz radio is using three ''[[Skyworks]]'' (''[[SiGe]]'') [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=969 SE5003L] :5GHz Power Amplifier Modules (PAM).
A MAC label w/ a 78:19:F7 (''Juniper Networks'') OUI is affixed :to the EUT's main board in the FCC internal photos.
